#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "介绍"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "Gametype:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "Logic, Arcade"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of possible players:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>One</para>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kblocks; is the classic falling blocks game. The idea is stack the falling "
"blocks in a way that lines are completely filled. When a line is completed "
"it is removed, and more space is available in the play area. When there is "
"not enough space for blocks to fall, the game is over."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kblocks; gameboard"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Rotate the falling blocks, and fit them together to complete lines and clear "
"the playfield."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, falling blocks can be moved left or right using the &Left; or "
"&Right; arrow keys. The &Down; arrow key makes the block drop faster, and "
"the &Up; arrow key is used to rotate the block. The keys used for each game "
"action can be configured in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，可以使用左右键向左或向右移动下落块。向下键使块下降得更快，向上键"
"用于旋转块。用于每个游戏操作的键可以在<menuchoice><guimenu>设置</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>配置快捷键.</guimenuitem></menuchoice>菜单项中配置。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rules"
msgstr "规则"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "The rules are simple: just keep space for the blocks to fall!"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "When a new block cannot fall, the game is over."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Do not forget to check the preview area: it shows the next piece that will "
"be released."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "For additional points, try to remove several lines at once."
msgstr ""

